==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*[[ἄνθρωπος]] / anthrōpos / anth'-ro-pos
*From G435 and ὤψ ōps (the countenance; from G3700); manfaced, that is, a human being: 

===Noun===
'''ἄνθρωπος''' ''m''

# [[man]], [[human being]]
#:*Modern: [[άνθρωπος]]
# [[certain]], [[man]].

